//doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/src/alloc/rc.rs.html#2463\">Source</a></span><a href=\"#impl-Drop-for-Rc%3CT,+A%3E\" class=\"anchor\">§</a><h3 class=\"code-header\">impl&lt;T, A&gt; <a class=\"trait\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/ops/drop/trait.Drop.html\" title=\"trait core::ops::drop::Drop\">Drop</a> for <a class=\"struct\" href=\"latexml_engine/prelude/struct.Rc.html\" title=\"struct latexml_engine::prelude::Rc\">Rc</a>&lt;T, A&gt;<div class=\"where\">where\n    A: <a class=\"trait\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/alloc/trait.Allocator.html\" title=\"trait core::alloc::Allocator\">Allocator</a>,\n    T: ?<a class=\"trait\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/marker/trait.Sized.html\" title=\"trait core::marker::Sized\">Sized</a>,</div></h3></section></summary><div class=\"impl-items\"><details class=\"toggle method-toggle\" open><summary><section id=\"method.drop\" class=\"method trait-impl\"><a class=\"src rightside\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/src/alloc/rc.rs.html#2490\">Source</a><a href=\"#method.drop\" class=\"anchor\">§</a><h4 class=\"code-header\">fn <a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/ops/drop/trait.Drop.html#method.drop\" class=\"fn\">drop</a>(&amp;mut self)</h4></section></summary><div class=\"docblock\"><p>Drops the <code>Rc</code>.</p>\n<p>This will decrement the strong reference count. If the strong reference\ncount reaches zero then the only other references (if any) are\n<a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/alloc/rc/struct.Weak.html\" title=\"struct alloc::rc::Weak\"><code>Weak</code></a>, so we <code>drop</code> the inner value.</p>\n<h5 id=\"examples\"><a class=\"doc-anchor\" href=\"#examples\">§</a>Examples</h5>\n<div class=\"example-wrap\"><pre class=\"rust rust-example-rendered\"><code><span class=\"kw\">use </span>std::rc::Rc;\n\n<span class=\"kw\">struct </span>Foo;\n\n<span class=\"kw\">impl </span>Drop <span class=\"kw\">for </span>Foo {\n    <span class=\"kw\">fn </span>drop(<span class=\"kw-2\">&amp;mut </span><span class=\"self\">self</span>) {\n        <span class=\"macro\">println!</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"dropped!\"</span>);\n    }\n}\n\n<span class=\"kw\">let </span>foo  = Rc::new(Foo);\n<span class=\"kw\">let </span>foo2 = Rc::clone(<span class=\"kw-2\">&amp;</span>foo);\n\ndrop(foo);    <span class=\"comment\">// Doesn't print anything\n</span>drop(foo2);   <span class=\"comment\">// Prints \"dropped!\"</span></code></pre></div></div></details><details class=\"toggle method-toggle\" open><summary><section id=\"method.pin_drop\" class=\"method trait-impl\"><a class=\"src rightside\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/src/core/ops/drop.rs.html#267\">Source</a><a href=\"#method.pin_drop\" class=\"anchor\">§</a><h4 class=\"code-header\">fn <a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/ops/drop/trait.Drop.html#method.pin_drop\" class=\"fn\">pin_drop</a>(self: <a class=\"struct\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/pin/struct.Pin.html\" title=\"struct core::pin::Pin\">Pin</a>&lt;&amp;mut Self&gt;)</h4></section></summary><span class=\"item-info\"><div class=\"stab unstable\"><span class=\"emoji\">🔬</span><span>This is a nightly-only experimental API. (<code>pin_ergonomics</code>)</span></div></span><div class='docblock'>Execute the destructor for this type, but different to <a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/ops/drop/trait.Drop.html#method.drop\" title=\"method core::ops::drop::Drop::drop\"><code>Drop::drop</code></a>, it requires <code>self</code>\nto be pinned. <a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/ops/drop/trait.Drop.html#method.pin_drop\">Read more</a></div></details></div></details>","Drop","latexml_engine::prelude::LabelMappingHook","latexml_engine::prelude::font::Fontmap","latexml_engine::prelude::BeforeDigestClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::ConditionalClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::ConstructionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::DigestedReversionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::DigestionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::ExpansionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::FontClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::PrimitiveClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::PropertiesClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::ReplacementClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::FontTestClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::LigatureMatcher","latexml_engine::prelude::ReaderClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::ReversionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::common::BindingDispatcher","latexml_engine::prelude::alignment::OpenContainerFn","latexml_engine::prelude::alignment::CloseContainerFn","latexml_engine::prelude::alignment::OpenRowFn","latexml_engine::prelude::alignment::CloseRowFn","latexml_engine::prelude::alignment::OpenColumnFn","latexml_engine::prelude::alignment::CloseColumnFn","latexml_engine::prelude::definition::register::RegisterGetterClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::definition::register::RegisterSetterClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::definition::SizingClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::document::tag::TagConstructionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::ligature::LigatureClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::parameter::ReaderPredigestClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::parameter::DigestedReversionClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::rewrite::RewriteReplaceClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::rewrite::RewriteTestClosure","latexml_engine::prelude::rewrite::RewriteRegexpClosure"],["<details class=\"toggle implementors-toggle\" open><summary><section id=\"impl-From%3C%26%5BT%5D%3E-for-Rc%3C%5BT%5D%3E\" class=\"impl\"><span class=\"rightside\"><span class=\"since\" title=\"Stable since Rust version 1.21.0\">1.21.0</span> · <a class=\"src\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/src/alloc/rc.rs.html#2882\">Source</a></span><a href=\"#impl-From%3C%26%5BT%5D%3E-for-Rc%3C%5BT%5D%3E\" class=\"anchor\">§</a><h3 class=\"code-header\">impl&lt;T&gt; <a class=\"trait\" href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/convert/trait.From.html\" title=\"trait core::convert::From\">From</a>&